# Vendor Performance Intelligence Engine — backup cron schedule
#
# Daily at 02:30 UTC (off-peak; after `PartitionManagerJob` finishes at
# 01:00 and after `AllVendorsRescoreJob` at 02:00 — keeps backup window
# clear of heavy DB writes).
#
# supercronic accepts the standard 5-field cron expression. Output goes
# to stdout/stderr which the docker engine ships to its log driver.

30 2 * * * /home/vpi-backup/backup.sh
